      },
      "privateNotes": "",
      "publicNotes": "<p><strong>Role:</strong> the Lyrune-Quah's 68-year-old cleric of Desna — spry-minded, frail-bodied, and the party's <strong>living endorsement</strong> (+3 Respect Points for his support; +10 circumstance on the Flameford Diplomacy). He insists on travelling along to <em>witness</em> their deeds, fixates charmingly on the most wilderness-awkward PC, and may not be given a Lyrune-Quah escort (honor forbids). Keeping him alive is the party's unspoken burden — a second story award if he survives to the Sun Shaman's lore.</p>",
